---
description: File and Directory Organization
alwaysApply: true
---
- All source code must be organized by chapter in the source/ directory
- Each chapter directory must contain both .py and _test.py files
- Archive directory should only contain deprecated or moved files
- All static assets (images, icons) must be in appropriate directories
- No duplicate files should exist between root and content directories
- All generated HTML files should be in the root directory